Package: cblindplot
Title: Recolors Images to be Colour Blind Friendly
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: c(
  person("Elisa", "Thouverai", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "elisa.th95@gmail.com"),
  person("Duccio", "Rocchini", role = c("aut"), email = "duccio.rocchini@unibo.it"),
  person("Jakub", "Nowosad", role = c("aut"), email = "nowosad.jakub@gmail.com", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1057-3721")))
Description: Enables colour blind people to enter an image, specify their colour vision deficiency, and get a colour blind friendly plot as output.
  It applies PCA analysis to the input image colors, and colors the values of the main principal component using a colour blind friendly palette.
